spells.description:
Use: Channel to vent flames for 2 sec, dealing 1.9 million Fire damage split between all nearby enemies.

Mechanical enemies become Superheated, taking 91,388  additional Fire damage when struck by your next harmful ability. (2 Min Cooldown)

Equip: Your melee attacks have a chance to putt a bomb toward your enemy, dealing 123,668 Fire damage on impact.

When you exit combat, gain a burst of speed for 10 sec if your score is a Hole-in-One, Birdie, or Par.

Equip: Gain scendance every 8 seconds spent in combat.

scendance grants 89 of a random secondary stat for 15 sec, stacking up to 10 times.

This is a Nerubian embellishment.
